    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a functional option for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that may need some cosmetic and mechanical attention. The engine starts and runs, though it lacks the crispness of a newer model, and the transmission shifts through all gears but shows some age-related hesitation. Inside, the upholstery shows visible wear and some staining, while the exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door. Recent maintenance has kept it roadworthy, but the buyer should anticipate replacing the tires and addressing a minor oil seep in the near future.",
