    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the S54 platform, featuring its signature 3.2L high-revving inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a factory 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically pristine, the VANOS unit has been fully overhauled and rod bearings replaced with treated shells for long-term reliability. The chassis integrity is verified with documented subframe reinforcement, while the Getrag six-speed manual transmission offers precise shift gates and a positive clutch engagement. Handling is sharp via the M-Variable differential lock and refreshed bushings throughout. The exterior retains its factory luster with consistent paint meter readings across all panels, and the interior remains free of bolster wear or dash delamination. A definitive, investment-grade driver's car.",
