    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional 2019 Porsche 718 Cayman in Graphite Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage and presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint is flawless, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the black leather upholstery remains taut and supple, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma; the cabin has never seen smoke or pets. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a full Porsche dealership service history and only 12,000 gentle miles on the odometer. The 20-inch Carrera S wheels are free of any curb rash and are wrapped in near-new Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection and a 'like-new' driving experience.",
